vote.title: Authorize a one-year service contract for transportation services for persons experiencing homelessness for the Office of Homeless Solutions - Austin Street Center, most advantageous proposer of three - Not to exceed $340,000 - Financing:  General Fund ($250,000) and ARPA Homelessness Assistance and Supportive Services Program Fund ($90,000) (subject to appropriations)
